article.description: — Jordan Whitfield had 20 points as Campbell got past Longwood 64-58 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Whitfield scores 20 to carry Campbell past Longwood 64-58
article.linkText: Whitfield scores 20 to carry Campbell past Longwood 64-58
article.story: FARMVILLE, Va. -- — Jordan Whitfield had 20 points as Campbell got past Longwood 64-58 on Saturday night. Whitfield made 9 of 12 shots. Cedric Henderson Jr. added 19 points for Campbell (6-6, 2/3 Big South Conference). Justin Hill had 11 points and nine rebounds for the Lancers (2-11, 1-6). Juan Munoz also scored 11 points. Zac Watson had 10 points. The teams meet again today. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
